    "long_instructions": "## Travel Agent - Providing a Single Example\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a travel agent by adding a single example to help guide the AI's recommendation.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI to recommend a family destination by including **an example** vacation destination.\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the AI builds on your example to make a more specific or relevant suggestion.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Recommend a vacation destination for a family of four that enjoys outdoor adventures and cultural experiences. For example: \r\n>\r\n> \"The Bahamas offers beautiful beaches and family-friendly resorts.\" \r\n:::",
